---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="About Us | The Mission Behind Unix Timestamp Converter"
	description="Discover why we build precision developer tools. Learn about our privacy-first approach and our commitment to accurate Unix time tracking."
>
	<div class="content-container">
		<header class="page-header">
			<div class="badge">Our Mission</div>
			<h1>About <span class="text-gradient">Our Mission</span></h1>
		</header>

		<section class="prose">
			<p>
				In the world of modern software engineering, time is more than just a sequence of eventsâ€”it's the heartbeat of distributed systems, the anchor of data integrity, and the language of global synchronization.
			</p>
			
			<div class="highlight-box">
				<h3>The Problem</h3>
				<p>
					Developers often struggle with clunky, ad-filled, or imprecise time conversion tools that break their flow and risk data errors.
				</p>
			</div>

			<h2>Precision at Scale</h2>
			<p>
				The <strong>Unix Timestamp Converter</strong> was born out of a simple need: a fast, beautiful, and developer-first utility for handling POSIX time. We believe that even the simplest tools should feel premium and function with absolute reliability.
			</p>

			<div class="stats-grid">
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-value">Real-time</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Synchronization</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-value">Zero</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Data Collection</span>
				</div>
				<div class="stat-item">
					<span class="stat-value">100%</span>
					<span class="stat-label">Free Forever</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			<h2>Who We Are</h2>
			<p>
				We are a small team of passionate developers dedicated to building the "missing utilities" of the web. Our tools are designed to be lightweight, privacy-focused, and aesthetically pleasing, ensuring they complement your professional workflow rather than distracting from it.
			</p>

			<div class="cta-section">
				<p>Want to see what else we're building?</p>
				<a href="/tools" class="outline-button">Explore All Tools</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<div class="back-link">
			<a href="/">&larr; Back to Home</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.content-container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 2rem auto;
		background: var(--card-bg);
		backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
		padding: 4rem;
		border-radius: 32px;
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
	}

	.page-header {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 4rem;
	}

	.badge {
		display: inline-block;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.1);
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
		border-radius: 100px;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.2);
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
		font-weight: 900;
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.1;
		letter-spacing: -0.03em;
	}

	.text-gradient {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(var(--accent)), rgb(var(--accent-light)));
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
	}

	.prose {
		color: #8b949e;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	h2 {
		color: #fff;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	h3 {
		margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}

	p {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.highlight-box {
		background: rgba(var(--accent), 0.1);
		border-left: 4px solid rgb(var(--accent));
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 0 16px 16px 0;
		margin: 3rem 0;
	}

	.highlight-box p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		color: #c9d1d9;
	}

	.stats-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		margin: 4rem 0;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.stat-item {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 20px;
		border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
	}

	.stat-value {
		display: block;
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #fff;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: #8b949e;
	}

	.cta-section {
		margin-top: 5rem;
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 3rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
	}

	.outline-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--accent-light));
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 100px;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.outline-button:hover {
		background: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		color: rgb(var(--accent-dark));
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

	.back-link {
		margin-top: 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
		padding-top: 2rem;
	}

	.back-link a {
		color: #8b949e;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
		transition: color 0.2s;
	}

	.back-link a:hover {
		color: #fff;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.content-container {
			padding: 2rem;
		}
		.stats-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>
